docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:141:                  → SenseWeave processes as "The Instrument" voice
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:167:      → "The Eye" voice feeds SenseWeave
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:188:- The Theramini is the primary melodic voice
docs/20260402-cypherclaw-embodiment-prd.md:219:- Registered as "The Scribe" sensory voice
